{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"文档类型声明","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Doctype","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>在 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/HTML\">HTML</a> 中，文档类型 doctype 的声明是必要的。在所有文档的头部，你都将会看到\"<code>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</code>\" 的身影。这个声明的目的是防止浏览器在渲染文档时，切换到我们称为“<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Quirks_Mode_and_Standards_Mode\">怪异模式 (兼容模式)</a>”的渲染模式。“<code>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</code>\" 确保浏览器按照最佳的相关规范进行渲染，而不是使用一个不符合规范的渲染模式。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"general_knowledge","title":"General Knowledge","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Document_type_declaration\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Type Declaration</a> 维基百科的解释</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Quirks_Mode_and_Standards_Mode\">Quirks Mode and Standards Mode</a> 怪异模式（兼容模式）和标准模式</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技术参考","title":"<strong>技术参考</strong>","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document/doctype\">Document.doctype</a>, 一个返回 doctype 的 JavaScript 方法</li>\n</ul>","titleAsText":"技术参考"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"在 HTML 中，文档类型 doctype 的声明是必要的。在所有文档的头部，你都将会看到\"<!DOCTYPE html>\" 的身影。这个声明的目的是防止浏览器在渲染文档时，切换到我们称为“怪异模式 (兼容模式)”的渲染模式。“<!DOCTYPE html>\" 确保浏览器按照最佳的相关规范进行渲染，而不是使用一个不符合规范的渲染模式。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Doctype","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Doctype","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Doctype","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Doctype","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"문서 타입 정의","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Doctype","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Doctype","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"